snippet.title: STARL Metaverse - Warp Nexus Chat w/ Scott Brown & Obie!
snippet.description:
Wyrmbyte Games CEO Scott Brown gives me a rundown of some of the features of the upcoming Warp Nexus MMO coming to the STARL Metaverse!

I'll post the full walk around the Hub and Arena soon!!

*Apologies for the audio issues, working on that.
